snippet.title: Space Adventure: Season Preview
snippet.description:
🚀Into the depth of the galaxy, off we go!
Brand new season pass that launch you to space. Multiple new maps to challenge your skills. What's more? NEW THENIONS are coming to Thetan Rivals.
Ohhhh, and that's not it! Thetan Rivals is now available in 5 countries: Germany, Canada, Indonesia, Malaysia, and Thailand. Buckle up, my Thenions, 'cause it is a bumpy launch.
#RiseRivals #ThetanRivals #GoThenionGo #newupdate #newpatch
